=== Customize phone ===

 echo "lima-ecko" > /etc/hostname
 hostname lima-ecko
 ln -s /bin/bash4 /bin/bash
 mkdir /usr/share/applications/hildon.old

==== Sounds ====

 The files in folder "sounds" have been taken from the game "Uplink", which I bought. 
 

